[{"Code":"en","Title":"Payments API webhooks","Slug":"payments-api-webhooks","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"00500365-bc3d-4d53-8718-e96009db9ba2\">This table shows the types of webhooks available for your system to subscribe to.</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"1218\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:1218px;width:1218px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:406px;\"><col style=\"width:406px;\"><col style=\"width:406px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"1e75fd2b-9a6d-461f-84c9-4a520bcaf61a\">Data resource object</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"70aa5706-803c-4103-bbeb-5f26f4d22621\">Webhook event</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"3cecedcc-92d3-4c81-9fa9-1d027d2aa946\">Description</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"eb9617ed-8df7-4a40-9a91-358bf6b0f982\">Payment Request</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"749b3eba-039c-4dcd-be71-fa634a4570be\">payment_request.expiry</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"546800c1-0c47-4c9d-af73-3fb6e0c00346\">Event occurs when payment request created has expired. An expired payment request will no longer receive new payments. Note that race conditions can happen due to limitations of real time messaging.  </p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"e5bd1029-5ab0-4a67-afa5-779b91a60245\">Payment Token</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"bd441131-54c0-4c6e-85e7-f370e2458e6e\">payment_token.activation</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"d782e5ee-307e-42bd-bd7d-68858ea41ebf\">Event occurs when payment token creation was successful authenticated and confirmed by the payment channel.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"0ad70287-0c32-473b-9511-21ac92427daf\">Payment Token</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"e9155528-0a38-4b85-aad5-668072075f8e\">payment_token.failure</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"f1bebaa6-87cc-4c50-96c6-a3b73c9fd6d1\">Event occurs when payment token creation failed authentication and failed by the payment channel.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"2e2a9505-fbe7-4299-962a-c31153eb760a\">Payment Token</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"41218f3d-2618-4ca3-ac5d-521ee6fe422a\">payment_token.expiry</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"b351ac77-3ba4-44c8-8ec1-566ee0baf6eb\">Event occurs when payment token has reached its natural expiry period or when a card has passed its expiry date.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"28632f37-c7fe-4bf6-ac09-1ae7d0d53e7a\">Payment</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"a6003e13-bc30-4c8d-a64a-8a73d792e59b\">payment.capture</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"1bad9e43-a1db-4f9e-bea2-16b40411220c\">Event occurs when payment has been successfully collected and confirmed by the payment channel.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"f44802e6-06cc-4640-848f-e67d1a1bbab5\">Payment</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"acdc9775-8c9e-4003-815c-09812fc45e16\">payment.authorization</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"3069c76f-9761-4c97-bbc8-3395533bc06a\">Event occurs when payment has been successfully reserved on the end user account and confirmed by the payment channel.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"c9fc5fcf-d4c4-436c-933d-c6d40ef5efa2\">Payment</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"31914eab-be14-41b3-88ea-d14d4e216bc4\">payment.expiry</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"2b7a5592-1181-4aa1-bd17-66908e64acfc\">Event occurs when a successful payment authorization has expired.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"18680271-0e3c-4cc5-bc6e-b22dcb644dca\">Payment</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"36ea2f06-51d1-4515-85f5-fbfbe085a448\">payment.failure</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"208140b6-2ea6-4b6d-9658-b06448f5ac9f\">Event occurs when payment fails to be collected by payment channel.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"4d566a85-3cf5-4bda-9000-0eac49809a90\">Refund</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"3038f701-0312-4254-b948-6001bb4d1484\">refund.succeeded</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"06876403-8663-4d1a-bb56-67b465af0570\">Event occurs when refund was successful and  confirmed by the payment channel.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"43817821-5a66-4187-b19a-2c3b511768fd\">Refund</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"7189e03f-adbd-4c3d-bfe0-4e2f64c038ca\">refund.failed</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"c180146c-8738-43d6-a636-eac954b5eba0\">Event occurs when refund has failed and was  failed by the payment channel.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"f1fb7d73-0667-48d8-baaf-29fff2f16591\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Payments API webhooks","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Webhook Payments API","Slug":"payments-api-web-hooks","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpcc-mfgytd-002\">Tabel ini menunjukkan jenis webhook yang tersedia untuk sistem Anda.</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"1218\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:1218px;width:1218px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:406px;\"><col style=\"width:406px;\"><col style=\"width:406px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpcd-oau1sw-003\">Objek sumber daya data</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpcd-u12qmb-004\">Event webhook</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpce-6s6xlm-005\">Deskripsi</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpce-l1ftuw-006\">Request Pembayaran</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpce-f0hu7w-007\">payment_request.kedaluwarsa</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpce-ds4cbf-008\">Terjadi ketika permintaan pembayaran yang dibuat telah kedaluwarsa. Permintaan pembayaran yang kedaluwarsa tidak akan lagi menerima pembayaran baru. Perhatikan bahwa kondisi balapan dapat terjadi karena keterbatasan pesan waktu nyata.  </p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpce-59ehho-009\">Token Pembayaran</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpce-0txu7r-010\">payment_token.aktivasi</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpcf-tyie2x-011\">Terjadi ketika pembuatan token pembayaran berhasil diautentikasi dan dikonfirmasi oleh channel pembayaran.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpcf-r7q8pl-012\">Token Pembayaran</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpcf-flakcr-013\">payment_token. kegagalan</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpcf-ys8ybd-014\">Terjadi ketika pembuatan token pembayaran gagal autentikasi dan digagalkan oleh channel pembayaran.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpcf-j3rejk-015\">Token Pembayaran</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpcf-cbaasl-016\">payment_token.kedaluwarsa</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpcf-e6ji7q-017\">Terjadi ketika token pembayaran telah mencapai periode kedaluwarsa alaminya atau ketika kartu telah melewati tanggal kedaluwarsanya.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpcg-lwfpt8-018\">Pembayaran</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpcg-iwx4m5-019\">pembayaran.tangkap</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpcg-7c6q79-020\">Terjadi ketika pembayaran telah berhasil dikumpulkan dan dikonfirmasi oleh channel pembayaran.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpcg-5ehisw-021\">Pembayaran</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpch-haf2hl-022\">pembayaran.otorisasi</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpch-k01yos-023\">Terjadi ketika pembayaran telah berhasil dipesan di akun pengguna akhir dan dikonfirmasi oleh channel pembayaran.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpch-4e4x4x-024\">Pembayaran</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpch-h80w3a-025\">pembayaran.kedaluwarsa</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpch-wt1ago-026\">Terjadi ketika otorisasi pembayaran yang berhasil telah kedaluwarsa.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpch-umbiy8-027\">Pembayaran</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpch-kox1sn-028\">pembayaran.kegagalan</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpci-vefxbe-029\">Terjadi ketika pembayaran belum gagal untuk ditagih oleh channel pembayaran.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpci-kzffsu-030\">Pengembalian dana</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpci-ce322h-031\">pengembalian dana.berhasil</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpci-fn890j-032\">Terjadi ketika pengembalian dana berhasil dan dikonfirmasi channel pembayaran.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpci-0zhqin-033\">Pengembalian dana</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpci-ev09pa-034\">pengembalian dana.gagal</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpci-up1auf-035\">Terjadi ketika pengembalian dana gagal dan digagalkan oleh channel pembayaran.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mc7kqpci-7vzbm2-036\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Webhook Payments API","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"Webhooks ของ Payments API","Slug":"payments-api-web-hooks","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"00500365-bc3d-4d53-8718-e96009db9ba2\">ตารางนี้แสดงประเภทของ webhook ที่ระบบของคุณสามารถสมัครรับข้อมูลได้</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"1218\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:1218px;width:1218px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:406px;\"><col style=\"width:406px;\"><col style=\"width:406px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"1e75fd2b-9a6d-461f-84c9-4a520bcaf61a\">อ็อบเจกต์ทรัพยากรข้อมูล</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"70aa5706-803c-4103-bbeb-5f26f4d22621\">อีเวนต์ Webhook</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"3cecedcc-92d3-4c81-9fa9-1d027d2aa946\">คำอธิบาย</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"eb9617ed-8df7-4a40-9a91-358bf6b0f982\">คำขอชำระเงิน (Payment Request)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"749b3eba-039c-4dcd-be71-fa634a4570be\">payment_request.expiry</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"546800c1-0c47-4c9d-af73-3fb6e0c00346\">อีเวนต์นี้เกิดขึ้นเมื่อคำขอชำระเงินที่สร้างขึ้นหมดอายุ คำขอชำระเงินที่หมดอายุแล้วจะไม่สามารถรับการชำระเงินใหม่ได้อีกต่อไป โปรดทราบว่าอาจเกิด race conditions ขึ้นได้เนื่องจากข้อจำกัดของการส่งข้อความแบบ real time</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"e5bd1029-5ab0-4a67-afa5-779b91a60245\">โทเค็นการชำระเงิน (Payment Token)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"bd441131-54c0-4c6e-85e7-f370e2458e6e\">payment_token.activation</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"d782e5ee-307e-42bd-bd7d-68858ea41ebf\">อีเวนต์นี้เกิดขึ้นเมื่อการสร้างโทเค็นการชำระเงินได้รับการยืนยันตัวตนสำเร็จและได้รับการยืนยันจากช่องทางการชำระเงิน</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"0ad70287-0c32-473b-9511-21ac92427daf\">โทเค็นการชำระเงิน (Payment Token)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"e9155528-0a38-4b85-aad5-668072075f8e\">payment_token.failure</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"f1bebaa6-87cc-4c50-96c6-a3b73c9fd6d1\">อีเวนต์นี้เกิดขึ้นเมื่อการสร้างโทเค็นการชำระเงินล้มเหลวในการยืนยันตัวตนและล้มเหลวโดยช่องทางการชำระเงิน</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"2e2a9505-fbe7-4299-962a-c31153eb760a\">โทเค็นการชำระเงิน (Payment Token)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"41218f3d-2618-4ca3-ac5d-521ee6fe422a\">payment_token.expiry</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"b351ac77-3ba4-44c8-8ec1-566ee0baf6eb\">อีเวนต์นี้เกิดขึ้นเมื่อโทเค็นการชำระเงินหมดอายุตามระยะเวลาที่กำหนด หรือเมื่อบัตรหมดอายุ</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"28632f37-c7fe-4bf6-ac09-1ae7d0d53e7a\">การชำระเงิน (Payment)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"a6003e13-bc30-4c8d-a64a-8a73d792e59b\">payment.capture</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"1bad9e43-a1db-4f9e-bea2-16b40411220c\">อีเวนต์นี้เกิดขึ้นเมื่อการชำระเงินได้รับการเรียกเก็บสำเร็จและได้รับการยืนยันจากช่องทางการชำระเงิน</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"f44802e6-06cc-4640-848f-e67d1a1bbab5\">การชำระเงิน (Payment)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"acdc9775-8c9e-4003-815c-09812fc45e16\">payment.authorization</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"3069c76f-9761-4c97-bbc8-3395533bc06a\">อีเวนต์นี้เกิดขึ้นเมื่อการชำระเงินได้รับการสำรองไว้ในบัญชีของผู้ใช้ปลายทางสำเร็จและได้รับการยืนยันจากช่องทางการชำระเงิน</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"c9fc5fcf-d4c4-436c-933d-c6d40ef5efa2\">การชำระเงิน (Payment)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"31914eab-be14-41b3-88ea-d14d4e216bc4\">payment.expiry</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"2b7a5592-1181-4aa1-bd17-66908e64acfc\">อีเวนต์นี้เกิดขึ้นเมื่อการอนุมัติการชำระเงินที่สำเร็จหมดอายุ</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"18680271-0e3c-4cc5-bc6e-b22dcb644dca\">การชำระเงิน (Payment)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"36ea2f06-51d1-4515-85f5-fbfbe085a448\">payment.failure</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"208140b6-2ea6-4b6d-9658-b06448f5ac9f\">อีเวนต์นี้เกิดขึ้นเมื่อการชำระเงินล้มเหลวในการเรียกเก็บโดยช่องทางการชำระเงิน</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"4d566a85-3cf5-4bda-9000-0eac49809a90\">การคืนเงิน (Refund)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"3038f701-0312-4254-b948-6001bb4d1484\">refund.succeeded</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"06876403-8663-4d1a-bb56-67b465af0570\">อีเวนต์นี้เกิดขึ้นเมื่อการคืนเงินสำเร็จและได้รับการยืนยันจากช่องทางการชำระเงิน</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"43817821-5a66-4187-b19a-2c3b511768fd\">การคืนเงิน (Refund)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"7189e03f-adbd-4c3d-bfe0-4e2f64c038ca\">refund.failed</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"c180146c-8738-43d6-a636-eac954b5eba0\">อีเวนต์นี้เกิดขึ้นเมื่อการคืนเงินล้มเหลวและล้มเหลวโดยช่องทางการชำระเงิน</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"f1fb7d73-0667-48d8-baaf-29fff2f16591\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Webhooks ของ Payments API","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"webhooks de Payments API","Slug":"payments-api-webhooks","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"00500365-bc3d-4d53-8718-e96009db9ba2\">Esta tabla muestra los tipos de webhooks disponibles a los que su sistema puede suscribirse.</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"1218\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:1218px;width:1218px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:406px;\"><col style=\"width:406px;\"><col style=\"width:406px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"1e75fd2b-9a6d-461f-84c9-4a520bcaf61a\">Objeto de recurso de datos</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"70aa5706-803c-4103-bbeb-5f26f4d22621\">Webhook event</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"3cecedcc-92d3-4c81-9fa9-1d027d2aa946\">Descripción</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"eb9617ed-8df7-4a40-9a91-358bf6b0f982\">Solicitud de Pago</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"749b3eba-039c-4dcd-be71-fa634a4570be\">payment_request.expiry</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"546800c1-0c47-4c9d-af73-3fb6e0c00346\">El evento ocurre cuando la solicitud de pago creada ha expirado. Una solicitud de pago expirada ya no recibirá nuevos pagos. Tenga en cuenta que pueden ocurrir condiciones de carrera (race conditions) debido a las limitaciones de la mensajería en tiempo real. </p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"e5bd1029-5ab0-4a67-afa5-779b91a60245\">Payment Token</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"bd441131-54c0-4c6e-85e7-f370e2458e6e\">payment_token.activation</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"d782e5ee-307e-42bd-bd7d-68858ea41ebf\">El evento ocurre cuando la creación del Payment Token fue autenticada exitosamente y confirmada por el canal de pago.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"0ad70287-0c32-473b-9511-21ac92427daf\">Payment Token</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"e9155528-0a38-4b85-aad5-668072075f8e\">payment_token.failure</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"f1bebaa6-87cc-4c50-96c6-a3b73c9fd6d1\">El evento ocurre cuando la creación del Payment Token falló la autenticación y fue fallida por el canal de pago.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"2e2a9505-fbe7-4299-962a-c31153eb760a\">Payment Token</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"41218f3d-2618-4ca3-ac5d-521ee6fe422a\">payment_token.expiry</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"b351ac77-3ba4-44c8-8ec1-566ee0baf6eb\">El evento ocurre cuando el Payment Token ha alcanzado su período de expiración natural o cuando una tarjeta ha pasado su fecha de expiración.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"28632f37-c7fe-4bf6-ac09-1ae7d0d53e7a\">Pago</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"a6003e13-bc30-4c8d-a64a-8a73d792e59b\">payment.capture</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"1bad9e43-a1db-4f9e-bea2-16b40411220c\">El evento ocurre cuando el pago ha sido cobrado exitosamente y confirmado por el canal de pago.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"f44802e6-06cc-4640-848f-e67d1a1bbab5\">Pago</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"acdc9775-8c9e-4003-815c-09812fc45e16\">payment.authorization</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"3069c76f-9761-4c97-bbc8-3395533bc06a\">El evento ocurre cuando el pago ha sido reservado exitosamente en la cuenta del usuario final y confirmado por el canal de pago.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"c9fc5fcf-d4c4-436c-933d-c6d40ef5efa2\">Pago</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"31914eab-be14-41b3-88ea-d14d4e216bc4\">payment.expiry</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"2b7a5592-1181-4aa1-bd17-66908e64acfc\">El evento ocurre cuando una autorización de pago exitosa ha expirado.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"18680271-0e3c-4cc5-bc6e-b22dcb644dca\">Pago</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"36ea2f06-51d1-4515-85f5-fbfbe085a448\">payment.failure</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"208140b6-2ea6-4b6d-9658-b06448f5ac9f\">El evento ocurre cuando el pago no puede ser cobrado por el canal de pago.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"4d566a85-3cf5-4bda-9000-0eac49809a90\">Reembolso</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"3038f701-0312-4254-b948-6001bb4d1484\">refund.succeeded</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"06876403-8663-4d1a-bb56-67b465af0570\">El evento ocurre cuando el reembolso fue exitoso y confirmado por el canal de pago.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"43817821-5a66-4187-b19a-2c3b511768fd\">Reembolso</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"7189e03f-adbd-4c3d-bfe0-4e2f64c038ca\">refund.failed</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"c180146c-8738-43d6-a636-eac954b5eba0\">El evento ocurre cuando el reembolso ha fallado y fue fallido por el canal de pago.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"f1fb7d73-0667-48d8-baaf-29fff2f16591\"></p>","SeoTitle":"webhooks de Payments API","Description":null}]